  "texts": [
    "This research is a call for balance and honesty in AI news reporting and not an exercise aimed at discrediting all reporting on the dangers of AI.",
    "Genuine reporting on the factual risks of AI must be encouraged, and sensationalism, along with AI-fear mongering, needs to be avoided.",
